The Lunastone
By Craig Dutton (c) 2014

Your name is Raiphus Drell and you live with your daughter Vessa on the island of Neos. This island is amongst many others residing on a far distant ocean planet called Aquana.

As a humble botanist you and Vessa live a peaceful life since your wife, Lyssa died ten years ago this week. She was murdered by your insane brother, Krelos.

Coming back from a trip you find Vessa missing! Your communicator has just sent you a message. It's from your brother, Krelos. He demands you to steal the Lunastone for him or Vessa dies!

The ancestors created the Lunastone centuries ago but when it was activated they realized they had a terrible weapon and locked it up in the Crystal Tower located on a secret island.

Your mission is to find this island, get in to the Crystal Tower and steal the Lunastone otherwise Vessa will be killed!

It seems improbable but Vessa's life depends on your success! Good luck.

Landing platform
You are on the island of Neos - your home. The platform is just like the other rooms of your home and are raised on platforms high above the jungle island.
You can go south.
You can see a metal plate and a flying craft.
