> give shadow ivy to veech
He eats the ivy then feels odd. He runs away being violently ill.
> rub floating sphere

> rub floating sphere
A vision appears in the sphere.

You are on Neos and laughing at a joke Lyssa, your wife, just told you. It's a cold night and Vessa is two years old playing with a toy Rocscraw. It's her favourite. Suddenly the door bursts open and your brother Krelos stands before you; a madness in his eyes. He looks towards Lyssa and tries to grab her. You intervene, a pot smashes on the floor, Vessa starts crying and in the struggle Krelos pushes Lyssa to the ground. Blood seeps from a deep gash from Lyssa's head. Krelos flees and you fall to your kness next to your dead wife.

Vessa's screams fade into the distance...
The vision changes.

Five years on and a seven year old Vessa is reading out loud to you. You notice a new message on your communicator. It tells you that Krelos will be executed tonight. His appeal failed. You won't be attending...
Another swirl, another vision.

Krelos had escaped his execution and is on the run.

Vessa is now 12 years old and you leave her for an hour or so on her own while you explore Neos for rare plants.

When you return Vessa had gone!

Your communicator sent you a new mesage and you read: I HAVE YOUR DAUGHTER, BROTHER. STEAL THE LUNASTONE FOR ME OR VESSA DIES. WHEN YOU GET THE STONE AWAIT FUTHER INSTRUCTIONS, KRELOS...
The vision changes one last time.

You are standing in a vault. You move a hidden wall panel and it reveals a keypad. The number you enter is the total value of the X and Y co-ordinates of Q'rel. You take the Lunastone...

