You can see Krelos and Vessa.
> speak to krelos

> speak to krelos
'Give me the Lunastone, brother and I'll give you back Vessa.' he grins. His mad eyes burn into you.
> speak to vessa

> speak to vessa
'I love you, Dada.' she smiles but you can see her eyes are sore from crying.
> use lunastone on krelos

> use lunastone on krelos

Nothing happens...

Darkness descends...

The Lunastone starts to hum and glows a bright white light. Suddenly a huge blast of energy shoots out of the stone and hits Krelos squarely in the chest. As the particles in his body disassemble his mad eyes stare at you with sadness...

What seems like an age the Lunastone lies silent once more and you look to the shadows. Vessa appears smiling back at you. She runs to embrace you and you hold her tight not wanting to let her go ever again.

As you make your way back to the flying craft you wonder what to do with the Lunastone? It would make a great paperweight.

'Are we going home now, Dadda?' asks Vessa looking up at you.

'Yes, my sweet.' you smile as you look down at her, 'We are most certainly going home!'

The End
